End
-> END

=== gotoTarget
Goto successful
-> DONE

=== function decreaseTestValue(x) ===
    { testValue < x:
    	~ testValue = 0
    - else:
    	~ testValue = testValue - x
    }

=== function testEvaluation(x, y) ===
   This is function output.
   Test values are {x} {y}
   ~ temp output = "" 
   ~ output = "testValue = {x} - {y}"
   ~ return output